emuInput.TitMainTitle: Two women, possibly including singer Catherine Wallace on right, holding cake in interior with two tone walls
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline for image possibly published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 31, 1959, pg. 1, reads: "The Winner! - Catherine Wallace of Pittsburgh, who beautiful soprano voice has delighted hundreds in local concerts, won first place in the annual Marian Anderson Auditions last week in Philadelphia. She is a student at the Juilliard School of Music."
